flowchart TD
  START(["진입 · /products/coupons"]) --> URL["useListState (IA-13 URL 쿼리스트링)<br/>?issue=all|amount|percent|free_shipping<br/>?q= (쿠폰명·코드, IME 안전 COMP-10)<br/>parseFilter(..., COUPON_FILTER_VALUES, 'all')"]
